OL,3,CChildren under five and more working
OL,4,Chouseholds facing hunger in UK ` report
OL,6,FMore than a quarter of children in the
OL,7,FUK are growing up in households facing
OL,8,Fhunger, according to major research by
OL,9,Fa food bank network which is insisting
OL,10,Fthe two-child benefit cap must be
OL,11,Fscrapped.
OL,13,FTrussell said its data showed 27% of
OL,14,Fchildren were growing up in food
OL,15,Finsecure households ` where they had
OL,16,Fto go without or cut back on quality
OL,17,For quantity of food because they could
OL,18,Fnot afford it.
