OL,3,CChildren under five and more working
OL,4,Chouseholds facing hunger in UK ` report
OL,6,FAbout three in 10 (31%) children aged
OL,7,Ffive and under were likely to be in
OL,8,Fthis situation, according to the
OL,9,Fcharity's latest Hunger in the UK
OL,10,Freport.
OL,12,FThe data, from mid 2024, paints a
OL,13,Fpicture of the situation with hunger
OL,14,Fin the UK when Labour came into
OL,15,FGovernment and the charity said there
OL,16,Fare no signs things have improved
OL,17,Fsince then, with living costs having
OL,18,Fcontinued to rise.
