OL,3,CChildren under five and more working
OL,4,Chouseholds facing hunger in UK ` report
OL,6,FThe report ` based on a Trussell
OL,7,Fanalysis of an Ipsos survey of almost
OL,8,F4,000 adults referred to UK food banks
OL,9,F` also showed paid work was no
OL,10,Fguarantee of food security, with 30%
OL,11,Fof people referred to food banks from
OL,12,Fworking households in mid 2024, up
OL,13,Ffrom 24% in 2022.
OL,15,FThe data comes ahead of the
OL,16,FGovernment's strategy on tackling
OL,17,Fchild poverty, which is expected to be
OL,18,Fpublished this autumn, having been
OL,19,Fdelayed from spring.
