OL,3,CChildren under five and more working
OL,4,Chouseholds facing hunger in UK ` report
OL,6,FAmong its recommendations, Trussell
OL,7,Frepeated a call for the two-child
OL,8,Fbenefit limit to be done away with,
OL,9,Festimating this would lift around
OL,10,F670,000 people out of severe hardship,
OL,11,Fincluding 470,000 children, by 2026/27.
OL,13,FOverall, the number of people facing
OL,14,Ffood insecurity across the UK grew,
OL,15,Ffrom 11.6 million people in food
OL,16,Finsecure households in 2022 to 14.1
OL,17,Fmillion people in 2024, including 3.8
OL,18,Fmillion children.
