OL,6,FSuccession actor Brian Cox, who has
OL,7,Fspoken about facing poverty in his own
OL,8,Fyouth, branded the report's findings
OL,9,Fshocking.
OL,11,FThe Trussell supporter said: "From my
OL,12,Fown experience, I know the harsh
OL,13,Freality of growing up in poverty and
OL,14,Fthe lasting impact it has. The
OL,15,Fconstant worry of how to put food on
OL,16,Fthe table is a feeling that never
OL,17,Fleaves you.
