OL,6,F"No child should have to know what a
OL,7,Ffood bank is, let alone need one. But
OL,8,Fshockingly, in the UK today, families
OL,9,Fwith young children face the highest
OL,10,Frisk of hunger and needing to turn to
OL,11,Fa food bank to get by.
OL,13,F"When 30% of people referred to food
OL,14,Fbanks in the Trussell community are
OL,15,Fpart of a household where someone is
OL,16,Fin work, it's clear that paid work
OL,17,Fisn't enough to protect people from
OL,18,Fhardship."
