OL,6,F"It isn't right that millions of
OL,7,Fpeople from all walks of life `
OL,8,Fincluding pensioners, disabled people,
OL,9,Fworking families, and carers ` are
OL,10,Fstruggling to make ends meet. Nobody
OL,11,Fin the UK should face hunger."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,14,FWork and Pensions said: "This
OL,15,FGovernment is determined to tackle the
OL,16,Funacceptable rise in food bank
OL,17,Fdependence.
